metadata.name: 444 - What's in store?
metadata.description:
In celebration of the 1-year anniversary of the Web3 Warriors podcast, we are minting this first NFT for the show. This is a commemorative NFT that will grant holders VIP access to any web3 event that Web3 Warriors is hosting or sponsoring in the future. 

We are tied in with a few DAOs and continue to explore new ways to activate our brand in the real world and the metaverse. üí• Looking forward to 2023! Thank you for supporting the Web3 Warriors mission - to promote the new web3 creator economy. üôèüèæ

Follow Web3 Warriors on your favourite podcast network. Airing live every Saturday.
